Khaoula .H,2026-01-29,"I returned my Lenovo order in full compliance with their return instructions and used the return label provided. The courier confirms the item was returned to the sender, yet over two months later, Lenovo has still not issued the refund.Despite multiple follow-ups and providing clear proof of return, I have received no resolution and no meaningful response from customer service.I fulfilled my responsibilities as a customer. Lenovo has not fulfilled theirs.After more than two months of being ignored, I have been forced to escalate the matter through PayPal and my bank, which should never be necessary for a straightforward return.This experience reflects extremely poor after-sales support and a lack of accountability. I would strongly caution others against ordering directly from Lenovo."
Gustavo Soares,2026-01-22,"I have been in an ongoing dispute with Lenovo for over 515 days, starting on August 14, 2024, regarding a laptop that has never functioned properly.Since then, Lenovo has opened at least four repair cases. The device has been sent back and forth multiple times, spent most of the year in Lenovo’s possession, and the issues were never permanently resolved. At one point, the device was even lost during transport.Lenovo eventually provided a replacement unit, which also turned out to be defective from the first use, leading to yet another repair case. Despite the product being under warranty the entire time, I was never allowed to benefit from the warranty in a normal or effective way.Lenovo later promised a commercial solution in writing, but proceeded with unauthorized repairs instead, contradicting their own statements. The device was finally returned to me severely damaged, improperly packaged, missing the charger, and completely unusable.Lenovo has repeatedly made promises (including via Instagram) to escalate my case and contact me, but these promises were never fulfilled. They also refused to provide the contact details of the consumer mediator, despite multiple explicit requests.After more than a year of procedures, delays, and broken commitments, Lenovo has now closed my case without providing a lawful and respectful solution. This experience has caused significant personal and professional harm. I strongly advise caution."
Romano Jackson Marie,2026-01-22,"Honestly, based on my experience buying a Lenovo laptop online, I received a Lenovo laptop as a gift from my partner and only started using it after 3 months. Then I noticed a white spot on the screen. However, Lenovo refused to provide the warranty that I should have been eligible for, and even claimed it was caused by external damage. Thank you, Lenovo Indonesia! I’m done with Lenovo."
LEON,2026-01-22,Absolute rubbish.  Whilst the hardware is great you cannot stop the software from defaulting to yahoo after selecting Google search engine and defaults back to edge and bing no matter how many times you change it.  Littered with ads too even with antivirus.  Too frustrating don’t waste your money
